parts.text:
Slurm

```json
{
  "application": "NAMD",
  "version": "3.0a9",
  "container": "Singularity",
  "container_image": "/shared/apps/bin/namd3_3.0a9.sif",
  "resources": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "tasks_per_node": 1,
    "cpus_per_task": 16,
    "memory": "64GB",
    "gpu": 1,
    "modules": [
      "rocm-5.4.2",
      "ucx-1.13.1",
      "ompi/4.1.4"
    ]
  },
  "environment": {
    "SLURM_JOB_PARTITION": "Ubuntu or RHEL8 or RHEL9 or SLES15 or CentOS8 or Rocky9",
    "SLURM_JOB_NODELIST": "Node list",
    "SLURM_JOB_ID": "Job ID"
  },
  "examples": [
    "jac/jac.namd",
    "apoa1/apoa1.namd",
    "f1atpase/f1atpase.namd",
    "stmv/stmv.namd"
  ],
  "command_line_arguments": [
    "+p1",
    "+setcpuaffinity",
    "--CUDASOAintegrate on",
    "+devices 0"
  ],
  "output_directory": "gpu1-$$-$SLURM_JOB_NODELIST-$SLURM_JOB_ID"
}
```
